<li><a href="https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/dynamic-choice/">Dynamic Choice</a> by Chrisoula Andreou.</li>
<li><a href="https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/events/">Events</a> by Roberto Casati and Achille Varzi.</li>
<li><a href="https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/holes/">Holes</a> by Roberto Casati and Achille Varzi.</li>
</ol>
